verbose_text: In the EA.hy926 endothelial cells, treatment with GPE at a concentration of 0.068 mug/ml significantly increased the GCS levels by 14% at the 24 h time point, while treatment with GPE at the concentration of 0.250 mug/ml led to a significant increase of 16.2% at 24 h time point compared to the control (XREF_FIG).
